item.title: test Open Research community
item.description: Test Open Research Community Test University is a Place. The open research community at Test is primarily located at the test campus and is eager to know open research advocates in the local area. We will be running a weekly “open science hacky hour” on the test campus, so if you want to learn more about open research, find new ways to open up your work, or just want to meet some new people, let us know and come along.
